title: Women Holding Hands Dark Skin Tone Medium Light Skin Tone
description: Two women holding hands, with one having a dark skin tone and the other a medium-light skin tone. Represents friendship, romance, or solidarity between women of different complexions.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this emoji beautifully depicts two women's hands clasped together, showcasing a harmonious blend of dark skin tone and medium-light skin tone with exquisite detail and realistic lighting.  The smooth gradients and soft rounded edges of their fingers convey a sense of connection, support, and solidarity, reflecting Apple's commitment to diverse representation and genuine human interaction in its emoji designs.
